2957918279256919733.Text: I have spoken with Azura, Queen of the Night Sky, at her shrine. She has tasked me to travel to and island near Dagon Fel and rid the island of the daedra Sheogorath has sent, and to bring back proof that he sent them. I may not disturb Rayna Drolan, the woman living there. If I can do this for her, she will reward me well.

309747949112402924.Text: I've killed the Golden Saint Staada, the most powerful of the daedra I found on the island.

2027152011292416279.Text: I've disturbed Rayna Drolan. Azura will not be pleased.

564729806158762256.Text: I returned to the Shrine of Azura to let it be known I have cleared the island of the daedra there and returned with proof that Sheogorath was behind the problems. Azura was grateful, and rewarded me with her Star, a magical soul gem of immense power.

2266052442035519898.Text: I returned to the Shrine of Azura. She was not pleased that I had disturbed the solace of Rayna Drolan, for she now must forfeit the wager.
